chunk_content: Data is reported only once annually at Q4. annual total: • TB_STAT_POS (See TB_STAT): Sum results across quarters. Disaggregations: Numerator Disaggregations: Disaggregate Groups Disaggregates ART Status by Age/Sex • New on ART: <1 F/M, 1-4 F/M, 5-9 F/M, 10-14 F/M, 15-19 F/M, [Required] 20-24 F/M, 25-29 F/M, 30-34 F/M, 35-39 F/M, 40-44 F/M, 45-49 F/M, 50-54 F/M, 55-59 F/M, 60-64 F/M, 65+ F/M, Unknown Age F/M • Already on ART: <1 F/M, 1-4 F/M, 5-9 F/M, 10-14 F/M, 15-19 F/M, 20-24 F/M, 25-29 F/M, 30-34 F/M, 35-39 F/M, 40-44 F/M, 45-49 F/M, 50-54 F/M, 55-59 F/M, 60-64 F/M, 65+ F/M, Unknown Age F/M Denominator Disaggregations: Disaggregate Groups Disaggregates TB_STAT_POS (See TB_STAT). TB_STAT_POS (See TB_STAT). Disaggregate Age Description: Age is defined as the age at the date of initiation on ART or current age, not the age descriptions & at the date of reporting.
